---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: "How fast can we see results?",
    a: "Most clients see clearer positioning and stronger engagement in the first 2-3 weeks. Pipeline results depend on consistency and offer strength."
  },
  {
    q: "Do you only work with LinkedIn?",
    a: "LinkedIn is the core channel, but we can repurpose into short-form, carousels, and ads once the content system is working."
  },
  {
    q: "What do you need from me to start?",
    a: "Your offer, target audience, past wins (even small), and 2-3 example creators/brands you like. We'll handle the system + execution."
  },
  {
    q: "Do you handle posting and scheduling?",
    a: "Yes, depending on the package. We can write, design, edit, schedule, and optimize."
  },
  {
    q: "What makes Cinemora different?",
    a: "We don't do random posting. We build a repeatable inbound system: strategy + creation + proof + iteration + conversion."
  }
];
---

<section class="relative py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-lime-400">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">We've got answers</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/60">Quick answers to the questions clients ask before booking.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      {faqs.map((item, i) => (
        <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 open:bg-white/10 transition">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">{item.q}</span>

            <span class="grid h-9 w-9 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-black/30">
              <span class="text-lime-400 text-xl leading-none group-open:rotate-45 transition">+</span>
            </span>
          </summary>

          <div class="mt-4 text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            {item.a}
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
      <a
        href="#book"
        class="rounded-xl bg-lime-400 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-black hover:opacity-90 transition"
      >
        Book a Strategy Call
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
